  <name>SkyTemple</name>
  <summary>ROM Editor for Pokémon Mystery Dungeon Explorers of Sky</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      SkyTemple: The Explorers of Sky ROM editor for maps, backgrounds and scripts, including an interactive debugger
      for the game's script engine.
    </p>
    <p>SkyTemple is in NO WAY affiliated with Nintendo, The Pokémon Company, Spike Chunsoft or any of their affiliates. This is an unofficial fan project.</p>
  </description>

